Package: gptchatteR
Type: Package
Title: R ChatGPR Wrapper
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Isin Altinkaya, ChatGPT
Maintainer: Isin ALtinkaya <isinaltinkaya@sund.ku.dk>
Title: R wrapper for the OpenAI GPT-3 model
Description: The chatgptr package provides an R interface to the OpenAI GPT-3 model, allowing users to generate responses to user input in a streaming manner. The package includes functions for setting up the API key, loading the GPT-3 model, and generating responses to user input with adjustable temperature and maximum token limits.
